{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01MghDuEDwFk3tJDEe4U4pjY","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the scenario much better. Looking at the test.yaml:\n\n1. The precondition probe checks if the StatefulSet exists or pods are running. If they are (inherited from a prior stage), it SKIPS the apply step.\n2. The apply step would normally:\n   - Delete/recreate the namespace\n   - Deploy the StatefulSet with v23.2 image (from resource files)\n   - Initialize the cluster\n   - Set `cluster.preserve_downgrade_option = '23.2'` to prevent auto-finalization\n\n3. HOWEVER, since stage 1 already had a running cockroachDB cluster, the probe SUCCEEDED (StatefulSet exists), so the apply was SKIPPED. \n\nThis means the preserve_downgrade_option was never set to '23.2'. But stage 1 already deployed resources with the image updated to v24.1.0, and the StatefulSet shows `--certs-dir` in its command, indicating TLS was enabled during stage 1. Now in stage 2, since the StatefulSet already exists, the precondition probe will skip the apply again.\n\nLooking at the current state, all pods are running v24.1.0 and the cluster version shows 24.1, which means the previous stage_02 agent already completed the upgrade—it updated the StatefulSet image, performed a rolling restart, and cleared the preserve_downgrade_option.\n\nThe issue is that the previous agent didn't write submit.txt, possibly due to getting stuck or being interrupted. So I need to verify all five criteria are met and then write submit.txt to complete the task. Let me double-check the StatefulSet resource to make sure everything is in order.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1971,"cache_read_input_tokens":41143,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1971},"output_tokens":27,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"816a0482-3c85-4513-b4d8-10bd2e6cb492","uuid":"b6da03ef-df43-48b7-af7f-0b2ff018d7b0","request_id":"req_011CcQNiNzUFNx5NMojottPr"}
